description: ClusterRegistrationToken is used by agents to register a new cluster.

ttl.description:
TTL is the time to live for the token. It is used to calculate the
expiration time. If the token expires, it will be deleted.

expires.description: Expires is the time when the token expires.

secretName.description: SecretName is the name of the secret containing the token.
